name: NFT CRYPTO MANIA
description: Collection Description Crypto mania Brasil started out as an informational meme for cryptocurrency enthusiasts on social media providing interesting information to followers. We love talking to cryptocurrency and blockchain leaders about what's trending in the market, NFT tokens could be the next big thing. And with that in mind we are launching our NFT token to bring this market trend to our followers. Sandro krunn started crypto mania in his college dormitory in Brasil when he realized that no one could explain what Bitcoin or blockchain was in less than ten minutes, and wanted to help people understand what they were putting their money into. With a background in marketing and humanities, she plunged headlong into the world of cryptography and discovered that she loved talking to people who worked in the industry and discovering the incredible projects that resulted from this technology that few people fully understood.Sandro grew up in Brasil, swimming at the national level for over a decade and making art in his spare time. Having grown up around the bizarre business environment that is technology, he feels at home with the incredible universe of cryptocurrencies.
